ems-center justify-between gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-bold tracking-tight\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-xs font-black\">AF</span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\">AlgoForge</span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Main\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/topics\">Topics</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors\" href=\"/search\"><span>Search…</span><kbd class=\"rounded border border-border bg-muted px-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono\">/</kbd></a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/dashboard\">Progress</a><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 hover:bg-muted text-foreground h-9 w-9\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><div class=\"container-af py-10\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Problems\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Largest Local Values in a Matrix II\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/largest-local-values-in-a-matrix-ii\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"Python\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/largest-local-values-in-a-matrix-ii/python\"}]}</script><ol class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems/largest-local-values-in-a-matrix-ii\">Largest Local Values in a Matrix II</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><span class=\"text-foreground font-medium\" aria-current=\"page\">Python</span></li></ol></nav><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-medium/15 text-medium\">Medium</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Largest Local Values in a Matrix II<!-- --> — <!-- -->Python</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"text-primary hover:underline\" href=\"/problems/largest-local-values-in-a-matrix-ii\">Full explanation</a> · <!-- -->Time <!-- -->O(n * m * logn * logm)<!-- --> · Space <!-- -->O(n * m * logn * logm)</p><div class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-code-bg text-slate-100\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-white/10 bg-black/30 px-2 py-1.5\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Language\"><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\">C++</button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors bg-white/15 text-white\">Python</button></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 px-3 text-sm text-slate-300 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 h-8\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Copy code\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div><pre class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed font-mono max-h-[32rem]\"><code># Time:  O(n * m * logn * logm)\n# Space: O(n * m * logn * logm)\n\n# 2d sparse table\nclass Solution(object):\n    def countLocalMaximums(self, matrix):\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;\n        :type matrix: List[List[int]]\n        :rtype: int\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;\n        # RMQ - 2D Sparse Table\n        # Time:  ctor:  O(N * M * logN * logM) * O(fn)\n        #        query: O(fn)\n        # Space: O(N * M * logN * logM)\n        class SparseTable2D(object):\n            def __init__(self, matrix, fn):\n                self.fn = fn\n                n = len(matrix)\n                m = len(matrix[0])\n                logn = n.bit_length()-1  # log2_floor(n)\n                logm = m.bit_length()-1  # log2_floor(m)\n                self.bit_length = [0]\n                for i in xrange(max(logn, logm)+1):\n                    self.bit_length.extend(i+1 for _ in xrange(min(1&lt;&lt;i, (max(n, m)+1)-len(self.bit_length))))\n                self.st = [[[[0]*m for _ in xrange(n)] for _ in xrange(logm+1)] for _ in xrange(logn+1)]\n                for r in xrange(n):\n                    for c in xrange(m):\n                        self.st[0][0][r][c] = matrix[r][c]\n                for j in xrange(1, logm+1):\n                    for r in xrange(n):\n                        for c in xrange((m-(1&lt;&lt;j))+1):\n                            self.st[0][j][r][c] = fn(self.st[0][j-1][r][c], self.st[0][j-1][r][c+(1&lt;&lt;(j-1))])\n                for i in xrange(1, logn+1):\n                    for j in xrange(logm+1):\n                        for r in xrange((n-(1&lt;&lt;i))+1):\n                            for c in xrange((m-(1&lt;&lt;j))+1):\n                                self.st[i][j][r][c] = fn(self.st[i-1][j][r][c], self.st[i-1][j][r+(1&lt;&lt;(i-1))][c])\n\n            def query(self, r1, c1, r2, c2):  # Time: O(fn)\n                i = self.bit_length[r2-r1+1]-1  # log2_floor(r2-r1+1)\n                j = self.bit_length[c2-c1+1]-1  # log2_floor(c2-c1+1)\n                return self.fn(\n                    self.fn(self.st[i][j][r1][c1], self.st[i][j][r1][c2-(1&lt;&lt;j)+1]),\n                    self.fn(self.st[i][j][r2-(1&lt;&lt;i)+1][c1], self.st[i][j][r2-(1&lt;&lt;i)+1][c2-(1&lt;&lt;j)+1])\n                )\n\n        n, m = len(matrix), len(matrix[0])\n        st = SparseTable2D(matrix, max)\n        result = 0\n        for r in xrange(n):\n            row = matrix[r]\n            for c in xrange(m):\n                x = row[c]\n                if x == 0:\n                    continue\n                r1, r2 = max(0, r-x), min(n-1, r+x)\n                c1, c2 = max(0, c-x), min(m-1, c+x)\n                tl = r-x &gt;= 0 and c-x &gt;= 0\n                tr = r-x &gt;= 0 and c+x &lt;= m-1\n                bl = r+x &lt;= n-1 and c-x &gt;= 0\n                br = r+x &lt;= n-1 and c+x &lt;= m-1\n                if max(st.query(r1, c1+(1 if tl or bl else 0), r2, c2-(1 if tr or br else 0)),\n                       st.query(r1+(1 if tl or tr else 0), c1, r2-(1 if bl or br else 0), c2)) &lt;= x:\n                    result += 1\n        return result\n</code></pre></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mt-20 border-t border-border bg-sidebar\"><div class=\"container-af py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-lg\">AlgoForge</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-xs\">Master coding interviews with patterns, roadmaps, and solutions</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Learn</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/grind-169\">Grind 169</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Interview</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/interview-preparation\">Interview prep</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/system-design\">System design</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/glossary\">Glossary</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Product</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about/attribution\">Attribution</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/sitemap-html\">Sitemap</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border\"><div class=\"container-af py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 justify-between text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->AlgoForge<!-- -->. Educational use only.</p><p>Solution code sourced under MIT from<!-- --> <a href=\"https://github.com/kamyu104/LeetCode-Solutions\" class=\"underline hover:text-primary\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">kamyu104/LeetCode-Solutions</a>. Explanations are original AlgoForge content.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/05kafvajig4wu.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[427423,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2fvm6eoqeukxu.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1ntn7efqc-iiw.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0plpm2axnqe9k.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[522016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2fvm6eoqeukxu.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1ntn7efqc-iiw.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0plpm2axnqe9k.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0a2gmow1_jiq0.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n10:I[168027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2fvm6eoqeukxu.js\\\",\\\"/_nex